OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772892686
OL,3,CCouple in tears as 'shed' removed from
OL,4,Cfront garden following council battle
OL,6,FA couple from Hastings have been
OL,7,Fforced to remove a "shed" from their
OL,8,Ffront garden following a three year
OL,9,Fbattle with their local council.
OL,11,FSteve and Julie Holden say they didn't
OL,12,Fneed to get planning approval for the
OL,13,Fstructure because the building is
OL,14,Fmoveable and should be classed as a
OL,15,Fcaravan.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
