PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772892686
OL,3,CCouple in tears as 'shed' removed from
OL,4,Cfront garden following council battle
OL,6,FA Hastings Borough Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "The council
OL,8,Frefused planning permission for the
OL,9,Fstructure and that decision has been
OL,10,Fupheld by the Planning Inspectorate on
OL,11,Fappeal.
OL,13,F"The Inspector's decision is final in
OL,14,Fplanning terms.
OL,16,F"Our understanding is that the owner
OL,17,Fis now making arrangements for the
OL,18,Fstructure to be removed."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
